title: Pet Friendly, Wood-burning Fireplace, Full Size Washer/Dryer
posting_body: WELCOME TO LIFE AT SpringfieldThis beautiful community is conveniently located in Renton, WA.
Enjoy this quiet neighborhood close to shopping, dining, parks and schools.
Less than 20 miles from both Seattle and Tacoma, the propertys great location offers easy access to freeways and major bus lines.
Our one- and two-bedroom open floor plans feature upgraded interiors with faux wood flooring, fireplace, washer/dryer, and a private deck or terrace.
Enjoy all the amenities the community has to offer including a clubhouse, game room and fitness center.
A convenient location, park-like setting, and great amenities make Springfield Apartments the perfect place to live.
